    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/31ebded3fca9e57fddb97b693c5888ff.avif?t=1771110481\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>故事：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演约翰——一名身负可耻过往的职业罪犯。当他在陌生旅馆醒来时，浑身是血、伤痕累累，更失去了过去八年的记忆，内心陷入剧烈挣扎。在噩梦与慢性疼痛的折磨下，约翰必须在疯狂中寻求真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/6fc81c676093108bc211c268042bef5e.poster.avif?t=1771110481\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/6fc81c676093108bc211c268042bef5e.webm?t=1771110481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/6fc81c676093108bc211c268042bef5e.mp4?t=1771110481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏玩法：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专为休闲玩家设计。这款心理惊悚游戏包含对话选择，无解谜元素，无支线任务，战斗系统简洁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/684b9f9a1b86a5dc6e610fa2498f8f7b.avif?t=1771110481\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>剧集式：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注：基础游戏即可畅玩全部6集！第2-6集升级了角色模型与角色纹理。</p>",
